				<h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-semibold">
					<span class="lang-en">6 masters stress-test the thesis</span>
					<span class="lang-zh">6 位大师挑战结论</span>
				</h2>
				<p class="portfolio-note">
					<span class="lang-en">
						Each roundtable invokes 6 guests — track expert, value, macro, institutional, and at
						least one dissenter. No dissent = research not done.
					</span>
					<span class="lang-zh">
						每次圆桌请 6 位嘉宾——赛道专家 / 价值派 / 宏观 / 制度 / 必含反方。没有反方 = 调研不够。
					</span>
